To build tailwind css and add custom file code in build file (not good approach)
>npx tailwindcss-cli build css/tailwind.css -o build/tailwind.css

To initialize package.json file
>npm init -y

To install tailwind, postcss, autoprefixer, and vite
>npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer vite

Now to generate tailwind css and post css config file
>npx tailwindcss init -p
